       Unlock Board Export 
       Ready for that presentation? Niice lets you take your board beyond the app by letting you download print-ready versions of your creations as well as zip files containing all your board's images 
     

     
       Unlock Dropbox Syncing 
       With Dropbox Syncing whatever you add in Niice gets added to your board's own folder in Dropbox. Oh, and it works the other way round too — whatever you add in Dropbox gets added to your board 
     

     
